title: PLYMOUTH SOUTH: Athletes of the Week
text: Posted Oct. 19, 2015 at 1:59 PM Updated at 2:05 PM Posted Oct. 19, 2015 at 1:59 PM Updated at 2:05 PM The Plymouth South Athletes of the Week are freshman Jillian Callahan from the girls cross country team and senior Dylan Anti from the football team. Callahan has been first or second in four meets so far this season. Anti has rushed for 595 yards in five games and scored five times. Courtesy photo Wicked Local Posted Oct. 19, 2015 at 1:59 PM Updated at 2:05 PM
